<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Za-za-zan!</i></b></font>

25
00:01:25,864 --> 00:01:29,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rakushou de funde ikeru ze, madamada</i></b></font>

26
00:02:14,144 --> 00:02:16,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I get it now, Nobuhiko.</b></font>

27
00:02:16,044 --> 00:02:19,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure enough, in a sense this car
could be a monster machine.</b></font>

28
00:02:19,984 --> 00:02:23,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even just taking it out for a
light spin, it got this kind of time.</b></font>

29
00:02:23,694 --> 00:02:27,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why I said this was about
something extremely simple.</b></font>

30
00:02:27,164 --> 00:02:28,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Weight, huh?</b></font>

31
00:02:28,694 --> 00:02:35,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes. One weapon that no opponent
has yet used is to be lightweight.</b></font>

32
00:02:35,164 --> 00:02:36,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the downhill stage,</b></font>

33
00:02:36,404 --> 00:02:39,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>being lightweight is the ultimate
weapon that breaks all rules.</b></font>

34
00:02:39,104 --> 00:02:42,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If we use that as our counterstrike,
and on a difficult course</b></font>

35
00:02:42,774 --> 00:02:44,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>specific to the Saitama area...</b></font>

36
00:02:45,744 --> 00:02:48,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...we will be able to beat
Project D's Eight-Six...</b></font>

37
00:02:48,944 --> 00:02:51,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...with our Cappuccino minicar!</b></font>

38
00:02:55,624 --> 00:02:58,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, that's a Ferrari racer for you.</b></font>

39
00:02:58,194 --> 00:03:00,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Personally, while I'm not entirely opposed,</b></font>

40
00:03:00,024 --> 00:03:04,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't much care for taking a car
sideways during corner entry.</b></font>

41
00:03:04,634 --> 00:03:08,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car has a shorter wheelbase,
allowing it to enter spin mode faster.</b></font>

42
00:03:08,804 --> 00:03:10,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I told you, didn't I? He's a fanatic.</b></font>

43
00:03:10,804 --> 00:03:14,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter what kind of car
or how narrow the road,</b></font>

44
00:03:14,074 --> 00:03:17,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>he'll always take it out sideways.</b></font>

45
00:03:17,814 --> 00:03:22,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Doing that, he can pin down a
car's quirks as well as its limits.</b></font>

46
00:03:22,614 --> 00:03:26,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's a lot like Akina's Eight-Six,
that same fanaticism.</b></font>

47
00:03:28,584 --> 00:03:30,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm really looking forward to this.</b></font>

48
00:03:30,324 --> 00:03:33,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The time has finally come to put a stop</b></font>

49
00:03:33,224 --> 00:03:35,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to the mighty Eight-Six's consecutive wins.</b></font>

50
00:03:35,624 --> 00:03:38,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come anytime, Project D.</b></font>

51
00:03:38,434 --> 00:03:43,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll show you the true power of a
united Saitama-Northwest Area team!</b></font>

52
00:03:40,604 --> 00:03:45,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Act 10: The Saitama Area's Ultimate Weapon"</b></font>

53
00:03:58,854 --> 00:04:01,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--I'm done.
--Good job.</b></font>

54
00:04:05,654 --> 00:04:07,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ya know,</b></font>

55
00:04:07,124 --> 00:04:11,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've noticed that something
about this car is always different.</b></font>

56
00:04:11,034 --> 00:04:13,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And a lot of work's been put
into it in ways ya can't see, right?</b></font>

57
00:04:13,704 --> 00:04:15,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, I guess.</b></font>

58
00:04:15,334 --> 00:04:18,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even the headlights have been
changed out for lighter ones. Somehow.</b></font>

59
00:04:18,934 --> 00:04:24,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If taken to this extreme, even a
kid's game stops bein' a game, huh?</b></font>

60
00:04:24,314 --> 00:04:26,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Takumi.</b></font>

61
00:04:26,814 --> 00:04:30,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm givin' ya the Eight-Six.</b></font>

62
00:04:30,054 --> 00:04:34,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're a workin' man now. Sharin' the car
fifty-fifty has gotta be inconvenient.</b></font>

63
00:04:34,824 --> 00:04:38,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess... But are you being serious?</b></font>

64
00:04:38,994 --> 00:04:40,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What, you're not happy?</b></font>

65
00:04:40,894 --> 00:04:45,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For myself, yeah. But what will you do?</b></font>

66
00:04:45,694 --> 00:04:50,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've already decided to buy
another car. A used one.</b></font>

67
00:04:50,374 --> 00:04:51,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What kind of car?</b></font>

68
00:04:51,734 --> 00:04:56,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One that's practical and
easy to drive. I'm gettin' old.</b></font>

69
00:04:56,344 --> 00:04:58,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Practical and easy to drive?</b></font>

70
00:04:58,514 --> 00:05:00,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That doesn't sound like something he'd say...</i></b></font>

71
00:05:00,984 --> 00:05:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You take care of changin' it into your name.
And startin' next year, you pay taxes on it.</b></font>

72
00:05:06,184 --> 00:05:08,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Okay.
--Of course...</b></font>

73
00:05:08,724 --> 00:05:12,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's assumin' the car
is still runnin' next year.</b></font>

74
00:05:12,594 --> 00:05:16,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course it'll still be running.
Don't say weird stuff like that.</b></font>

75
00:05:16,764 --> 00:05:21,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I really like this car. I want
to keep driving it forever.</b></font>

76
00:05:21,234 --> 00:05:26,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's all fine and good. Just make
sure you handle things properly.</b></font>

77
00:05:36,714 --> 00:05:39,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The course we'll be scouting
today is supposedly narrow</b></font>

78
00:05:39,614 --> 00:05:43,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and intersected by
occasional drainage ditches.</b></font>

79
00:05:43,894 --> 00:05:47,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Ah.
--Well, courses in Saitama prefecture</b></font>

80
00:05:47,064 --> 00:05:49,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>are apparently the same everywhere.</b></font>

81
00:05:49,064 --> 00:05:51,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--By the way, Keisuke...</b></font>

82
00:05:51,894 --> 00:05:54,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This may come across as
needless meddling, but...</b></font>

83
00:05:54,364 --> 00:05:56,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?</b></font>

84
00:05:56,104 --> 00:06:01,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought she was a pretty
decent lady. That girl. She's cute.</b></font>

85
00:06:01,244 --> 00:06:05,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And coming all the way to Akagi...
That was touching, don't you think?</b></font>

86
00:06:05,144 --> 00:06:06,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What is it you don't like about her?</b></font>

87
00:06:06,984 --> 00:06:09,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing, really.</b></font>

88
00:06:09,214 --> 00:06:12,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a matter of like or dislike.</b></font>

89
00:06:12,384 --> 00:06:18,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like I told her, I just want
to concentrate only on D.</b></font>

90
00:06:19,724 --> 00:06:22,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've always thought this, but...</b></font>

91
00:06:22,064 --> 00:06:28,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, I think your way of thinking
is too focused. Or rather, too linear.</b></font>

92
00:06:29,164 --> 00:06:30,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's like driving techniques, right?</b></font>

93
00:06:30,934 --> 00:06:33,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Instead of always just flooring the gas,</b></font>

94
00:06:33,404 --> 00:06:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>being brave enough to
take your foot off the pedal</b></font>

95
00:06:35,774 --> 00:06:38,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>can sometimes lead to increased speed.</b></font>

96
00:06:36,414 --> 00:06:40,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Reduce Speed"</b></font>

97
00:06:40,344 --> 00:06:44,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still, me trying to tell you
about driving techniques</b></font>

98
00:06:44,614 --> 00:06:47,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>sounds incredibly pompous, huh?</b></font>

99
00:06:52,194 --> 00:06:56,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, you don't have to stoically
push yourself to such extremes, do you?</b></font>

100
00:06:56,834 --> 00:07:01,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dating a girl could probably be a plus.</b></font>

101
00:07:01,304 --> 00:07:05,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The truth is, you like that girl, don't you?</b></font>

102
00:07:08,544 --> 00:07:13,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With that girl, things wouldn't turn out
like with your last girlfriend, right?</b></font>

103
00:07:13,014 --> 00:07:15,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>After all, she races too.</b></font>

104
00:07:15,214 --> 00:07:19,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not the point. You just don't get it.</b></font>

105
00:07:19,684 --> 00:07:22,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's not talk about this anymore.</b></font>

106
00:07:30,464 --> 00:07:32,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A union of the Saitama and Northwest areas?</b></font>

107
00:07:32,964 --> 00:07:37,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. Project D operates so
much like an organization</b></font>

108
00:07:37,234 --> 00:07:40,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that we're no match for
them if we act individually.</b></font>

109
00:07:40,244 --> 00:07:44,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The only way we can fight them is
through our network of associates, right?</b></font>

110
00:07:44,174 --> 00:07:50,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's why Nobuhiko and the others joined
together to form a temporary team.</b></font>

111
00:07:50,014 --> 00:07:51,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is that so?</b></font>

112
00:07:51,884 --> 00:07:56,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And the thing is, they need money,
so everyone's pitching in a little.</b></font>

113
00:07:56,724 --> 00:07:59,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoko, can you give some too?</b></font>

114
00:07:59,694 --> 00:08:03,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If that's what it takes...
Will 5,000 yen be enough?</b></font>

115
00:08:03,564 --> 00:08:06,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kyoko. Got a minute?</b></font>

116
00:08:17,274 --> 00:08:20,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Are you all right with this?
--With what?</b></font>

117
00:08:20,014 --> 00:08:23,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The collection to defeat Project D.</b></font>

118
00:08:24,584 --> 00:08:29,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With things coming to this, I'm going to
ask you straight up, whose side are you on?</b></font>

119
00:08:29,054 --> 00:08:30,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In terms of feelings.</b></font>

120
00:08:30,924 --> 00:08:32,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whose side?</b></font>

121
00:08:32,394 --> 00:08:36,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you feel kind of on the fence about it,
it's okay if you don't pitch in.</b></font>

122
00:08:36,394 --> 00:08:40,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nobuhiko and the others are
serious about beating Project D.</b></font>

123
00:08:40,534 --> 00:08:43,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you're not in it 100%,
you don't have to participate.</b></font>

124
00:08:43,974 --> 00:08:49,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not saying this trying to be mean.
You know what I'm talking about, right?</b></font>

125
00:08:52,744 --> 00:08:55,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey Kyoko, did you know?</b></font>

126
00:08:55,044 --> 00:08:57,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Takahashi brothers of Project D</b></font>

127
00:08:57,814 --> 00:09:00,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>are the sons of someone
who runs a huge hospital.</b></font>

128
00:09:00,324 --> 00:09:04,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Really? I didn't know that.</b></font>

129
00:09:04,124 --> 00:09:08,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're good-looking and have money to boot.</b></font>

130
00:09:08,294 --> 00:09:11,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You should think twice about that sort of guy.</b></font>

131
00:09:11,334 --> 00:09:12,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I'm just trash?</b></font>

132
00:09:12,994 --> 00:09:17,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, that's not what I'm saying.
But they're popular with the ladies.</b></font>

133
00:09:17,104 --> 00:09:22,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if you go chasing after a guy
like that, all you're going to get is hurt.</b></font>

134
00:09:22,344 --> 00:09:26,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm saying this for your own good.
You should snap out of this, and soon.</b></font>

135
00:09:32,154 --> 00:09:35,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No, I can't accept that.</i></b></font>

136
00:09:35,184 --> 00:09:38,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My darling is the only one for me!</i></b></font>

137
00:10:05,684 --> 00:10:09,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Coming along nicely, huh?</b></font>

138
00:10:09,124 --> 00:10:14,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Call it against the rules or whatever
you like, but I want to beat Project D...</b></font>

139
00:10:14,624 --> 00:10:17,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And this is the only way to do it.</b></font>

140
00:10:26,234 --> 00:10:30,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A change of title? For the Eight-Six?</b></font>

141
00:10:30,514 --> 00:10:33,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So what's your dad gonna do?</b></font>

142
00:10:33,214 --> 00:10:35,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll buy something else.</b></font>

143
00:10:35,044 --> 00:10:37,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whoa... Like what?</b></font>

144
00:10:37,184 --> 00:10:42,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He didn't say specifically, but he said
it'll be practical and easy to drive,</b></font>

145
00:10:42,524 --> 00:10:44,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>so maybe an automatic van or a minivan.</b></font>

146
00:10:44,724 --> 00:10:48,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you serious?! There goes his image.</b></font>

147
00:10:48,224 --> 00:10:53,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The man called the "legendary racer of Akina"
driving an automatic van or minivan...</b></font>

148
00:10:53,504 --> 00:10:57,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where's the harm? He is getting old and all.</b></font>

149
00:10:57,734 --> 00:11:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be nice if he got some old-man
car and just settled down.</b></font>

150
00:11:02,044 --> 00:11:05,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

151
00:11:02,174 --> 00:11:04,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Speaking personally.</b></font>

152
00:11:09,514 --> 00:11:10,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well...</b></font>

153
00:11:10,514 --> 00:11:13,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to be late for the
rendezvous, so I'd better get going.</b></font>

154
00:11:13,754 --> 00:11:16,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Break a leg, Takumi!</b></font>

155
00:11:16,184 --> 00:11:20,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll be going with Iketani and the
others to cheer you on tomorrow!</b></font>

156
00:11:39,274 --> 00:11:41,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Say, Fumihiro.</b></font>

157
00:11:41,584 --> 00:11:45,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This latest expedition could turn
out to be the greatest challenge</b></font>

158
00:11:45,084 --> 00:11:47,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara has yet faced.</b></font>

159
00:11:47,324 --> 00:11:53,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fujiwara? But all his races are tough,
one right after the other.</b></font>

160
00:11:53,324 --> 00:11:56,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That time he raced the Toudou School,
he went up against a pro racer.</b></font>

161
00:11:56,934 --> 00:12:02,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This could turn out to be even more difficult.</b></font>

162
00:12:02,604 --> 00:12:04,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Someone more difficult than a pro racer?!</b></font>

163
00:12:04,504 --> 00:12:08,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>His greatest enemy does not
necessarily have to be the driver.</b></font>

164
00:12:08,174 --> 00:12:10,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? What's that supposed to mean?</b></font>

165
00:12:10,414 --> 00:12:12,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'll understand soon enough.</b></font>

166
00:12:13,514 --> 00:12:17,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to sleep now. Don't wake
me until we reach our destination.</b></font>

167
00:12:17,484 --> 00:12:19,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay. Understood.</b></font>

168
00:12:19,914 --> 00:12:22,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His "greatest challenge"?</i></b></font>

169
00:12:22,484 --> 00:12:24,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Just what is that supposed to mean?</i></b></font>

170
00:12:40,604 --> 00:12:42,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're here.</b></font>

171
00:12:47,814 --> 00:12:51,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! We've been waiting for you. Eagerly.</b></font>

172
00:12:53,654 --> 00:12:55,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You remember me, right?</b></font>

173
00:12:55,784 --> 00:12:57,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yes, I remember you.</b></font>

174
00:12:57,394 --> 00:13:01,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This time it won't be me you're up against,
but I'm still looking forward to your race.</b></font>

175
00:13:01,864 --> 00:13:03,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? You!</b></font>

176
00:13:03,664 --> 00:13:06,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Forgive this old foe for coming
back under a new guise,</b></font>

177
00:13:06,464 --> 00:13:09,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but this time I'll be
participating from the sidelines.</b></font>

178
00:13:09,064 --> 00:13:13,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In any case, we'll open up the course now,
so race it as much as you like.</b></font>

179
00:13:13,174 --> 00:13:14,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

180
00:13:14,474 --> 00:13:16,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See you.</b></font>

181
00:13:20,584 --> 00:13:25,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a moisture to this wind.
There appears to be a 50% chance of rain.</b></font>

182
00:13:25,084 --> 00:13:27,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't say I'm too thrilled about the rain.</b></font>

183
00:13:27,824 --> 00:13:31,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So long as you etch the details of the course
into memory, there will be no problem.</b></font>

184
00:13:31,854 --> 00:13:36,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Concentrate. Your goal is
to make 50 runs by morning.</b></font>

185
00:13:36,494 --> 00:13:38,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right.</b></font>

186
00:13:38,194 --> 00:13:40,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

187
00:13:42,564 --> 00:13:46,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Standby prep complete. We're good, Keisuke.</b></font>

188
00:13:46,674 --> 00:13:48,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, let's go.</b></font>

189
00:14:09,624 --> 00:14:12,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She's not here, eh?</i></b></font>

190
00:14:56,914 --> 00:15:00,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wonder if Project D</i>
<i>has started racing by now.</i></b></font>

191
00:15:00,684 --> 00:15:05,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want to race right over there,</i>
<i>but I feel discouraged somehow.</i></b></font>

192
00:15:05,684 --> 00:15:11,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm like the bat in that</i>
<i>Aesop's fable I read as a kid...</i></b></font>

193
00:15:11,324 --> 00:15:15,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like I'm the only one without any friends.</i></b></font>

194
00:15:22,764 --> 00:15:25,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if it'll rain come tomorrow...</b></font>

195
00:15:25,104 --> 00:15:28,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Probably. Rain would be welcome.</b></font>

196
00:15:28,174 --> 00:15:31,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It would make the perfect
curves for Sakamoto.</b></font>

197
00:15:31,944 --> 00:15:34,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The worse that conditions get,</b></font>

198
00:15:34,144 --> 00:15:36,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the more effective our weapon,
lightness, will become.</b></font>

199
00:15:36,984 --> 00:15:42,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But if the rain gets too bad,
we'll have to cancel the race, right?</b></font>

200
00:15:42,454 --> 00:15:48,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I doubt it. All four cars are FRs, which
means they're on equal footing. Also...</b></font>

201
00:15:48,664 --> 00:15:52,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>These aren't the kind of opponents
who'd run away over something like rain.</b></font>

202
00:15:52,894 --> 00:15:55,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We couldn't ask for a more
perfect turn of events.</b></font>

203
00:15:55,864 --> 00:15:59,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If there is such a thing as fate, that
which could sway the course of a race...</b></font>

204
00:15:59,904 --> 00:16:03,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...then without a doubt,
it has turned in our favor!</b></font>

205
00:16:21,364 --> 00:16:23,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Gas it up. Ten liters will do.</b></font>

206
00:16:23,994 --> 00:16:25,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

207
00:16:25,764 --> 00:16:27,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke.</b></font>

208
00:16:27,204 --> 00:16:30,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once you're comfortable, race the latter
half of the course with your headlights off,</b></font>

209
00:16:30,404 --> 00:16:32,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>fog lights only.</b></font>

210
00:16:32,674 --> 00:16:35,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If it rains, visibility will worsen.</b></font>

211
00:16:35,274 --> 00:16:39,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This will be training to rely
not just on your eyes,</b></font>

212
00:16:39,244 --> 00:16:41,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but on your mental image of the course.</b></font>

213
00:16:41,544 --> 00:16:45,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A rain strategy, huh? Okay, I'll give it a try.</b></font>

214
00:17:12,974 --> 00:17:16,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sure enough, I worried about my darling...</i></b></font>

215
00:17:25,724 --> 00:17:27,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My darling's FD?</i></b></font>

216
00:17:27,324 --> 00:17:32,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Keep Out"</b></font>

217
00:17:36,504 --> 00:17:38,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want to touch it!</i></b></font>

218
00:17:55,824 --> 00:17:57,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>H-He showed up!</b></font>

219
00:17:57,794 --> 00:18:02,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Protected Forest"</b></font>

220
00:17:57,854 --> 00:18:03,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean I "showed up"?
That would be <i>you</i>!</b></font>

221
00:18:03,524 --> 00:18:06,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You scared me! I thought
my heart was gonna stop.</b></font>

222
00:18:06,934 --> 00:18:09,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you doing out here?</b></font>

223
00:18:09,664 --> 00:18:13,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well, I was taking a nap.
The race is tonight, you know.</b></font>

224
00:18:13,874 --> 00:18:18,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Th-That's right. Um, good luck!</b></font>

225
00:18:18,614 --> 00:18:21,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I need to sleep for tonight, but...</b></font>

226
00:18:21,714 --> 00:18:26,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once I wake up, I can't go back to sleep.
On top of that, now I'm hungry.</b></font>

227
00:18:26,384 --> 00:18:29,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you free right now?</b></font>

228
00:18:41,304 --> 00:18:42,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um...</b></font>

229
00:18:42,464 --> 00:18:45,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you come to places like this often?</b></font>

230
00:18:46,634 --> 00:18:48,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>"Places like this"?</b></font>

231
00:18:48,344 --> 00:18:49,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Casual dining restaurants and stuff.</b></font>

232
00:18:49,974 --> 00:18:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. All the time!</b></font>

233
00:18:53,074 --> 00:18:55,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's one of the basics, right? Street
racers go to casual dining restaurants!</b></font>

234
00:18:55,984 --> 00:18:58,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Y-Yeah, you're right!</b></font>

235
00:18:58,054 --> 00:19:04,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His family may own a big hospital, but he's</i>
<i>like a down-to-earth prince. What a relief!</i></b></font>

236
00:19:08,364 --> 00:19:11,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Keisuke's not here.</b></font>

237
00:19:11,194 --> 00:19:12,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder where he's gone.</b></font>

238
00:19:12,834 --> 00:19:16,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe he went to get something to eat.</b></font>

239
00:19:16,164 --> 00:19:17,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On foot?</b></font>

240
00:19:17,534 --> 00:19:20,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing we can do now.
Shall we go ahead and eat?</b></font>

241
00:19:20,604 --> 00:19:22,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, might as well.</b></font>

242
00:19:26,244 --> 00:19:30,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the weather stays nice, it kinda puts
you in the mood for a little hiking, huh?</b></font>

243
00:19:30,754 --> 00:19:33,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Hey, pass me a tea.
--Here.</b></font>

244
00:19:33,754 --> 00:19:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

245
00:19:35,424 --> 00:19:38,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Could you sleep?
--Two or three hours, I think.</b></font>

246
00:19:38,554 --> 00:19:42,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be best if you get some
rest after you're done eating.</b></font>

247
00:19:42,264 --> 00:19:46,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even if you don't sleep, closing your eyes
and resting will take away the tiredness.</b></font>

248
00:19:46,564 --> 00:19:47,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay.</b></font>

249
00:19:47,704 --> 00:19:52,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But I want to get in two
or three races if it rains.</b></font>

250
00:19:52,874 --> 00:19:57,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'd like to check which areas collect puddles
and whatnot while it's still daylight.</b></font>

251
00:19:57,374 --> 00:19:58,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

252
00:19:58,544 --> 00:20:01,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sure enough, it looks like
it could rain right now,</b></font>

253
00:20:01,714 --> 00:20:04,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>even though it hasn't gotten around to it yet.</b></font>

254
00:20:06,614 --> 00:20:11,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you always sleep in your car
when you're out for Project D?</b></font>

255
00:20:11,254 --> 00:20:16,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For the most part, yeah.
But we don't get much rest.</b></font>

256
00:20:16,094 --> 00:20:18,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Bucket seats are terrible for sleeping in.</b></font>

257
00:20:18,064 --> 00:20:22,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That sounds rough. Why not stay at
a bed-and-breakfast or something?</b></font>

258
00:20:22,004 --> 00:20:26,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We race until morning and
then sleep once it gets light.</b></font>

259
00:20:26,074 --> 00:20:28,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There aren't any bed-and-breakfasts
that'd give us a room then.</b></font>

260
00:20:28,644 --> 00:20:31,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh. I guess you're right.</b></font>

261
00:20:34,084 --> 00:20:37,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Now that I'm full, I've gotten kinda sleepy.</b></font>

262
00:20:34,614 --> 00:20:38,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Open 24 Hours"</b></font>

263
00:20:37,084 --> 00:20:39,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you say we head back?</b></font>

264
00:20:46,094 --> 00:20:48,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's started raining.</b></font>

265
00:20:50,764 --> 00:20:53,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What should I do? My darling fell asleep!</i></b></font>

266
00:20:59,474 --> 00:21:04,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Poor man. I'll make sure not</i>
<i>to wake him. Slowly, slowly...</i></b></font>

267
00:21:19,524 --> 00:21:23,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I wish time would stop for this moment.</i></b></font>

268
00:21:29,364 --> 00:21:33,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please God, make time stop for this moment!</i></b></font>

269
00:21:45,314 --> 00:21:49,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not good. It's really gotten wet.</b></font>

270
00:21:49,084 --> 00:21:51,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing for it but to prepare
for the worst and head out, eh?</b></font>

271
00:21:55,094 --> 00:21:58,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't race in rain like this.</b></font>

272
00:21:58,564 --> 00:22:01,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're crazy, brother,
and so are the rest of you.</b></font>

273
00:22:04,534 --> 00:22:06,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Doesn't look like it's gonna let up, does it?</b></font>

274
00:22:06,434 --> 00:22:10,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nope. Looks like it's going to
keep raining like this all night.</b></font>

275
00:22:10,204 --> 00:22:12,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's no way they'd cancel the race, right?</b></font>

276
00:22:12,444 --> 00:22:16,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I certainly doubt it.
Let's get ready to head out.</b></font>

277
00:22:16,844 --> 00:22:18,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yessir!</b></font>

278
00:22:30,394 --> 00:22:32,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Huh? Oh, no!</b></font>

279
00:22:32,594 --> 00:22:35,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I totally fell asleep!</b></font>

280
00:22:35,634 --> 00:22:37,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What time is it?</b></font>

281
00:22:37,434 --> 00:22:40,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Um... It's 6:00.</b></font>

282
00:22:40,744 --> 00:22:47,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was out for so long. But I've never slept
this soundly on any of our previous races!</b></font>

283
00:22:49,084 --> 00:22:53,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you all right? We've spent
half the day out here.</b></font>

284
00:22:53,414 --> 00:22:56,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sorry. You probably had
things of your own to do.</b></font>

285
00:22:56,754 --> 00:23:00,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, I'm fine! Don't even worry about that!</b></font>

286
00:23:00,124 --> 00:23:03,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I didn't have any errands or anything, so...</b></font>

287
00:23:03,564 --> 00:23:05,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you.</b></font>

288
00:23:08,234 --> 00:23:10,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay, I have to go.</b></font>

289
00:23:13,004 --> 00:23:16,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is bad. I still have to
finalize the car's settings!</b></font>

290
00:23:27,114 --> 00:23:28,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thank you!</b></font>

291
00:23:43,034 --> 00:23:45,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ah! Here they come!</b></font>

292
00:23:50,874 --> 00:23:52,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A Cappuccino?!</b></font>

293
00:23:58,814 --> 00:24:04,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke, more and more I've come
to understand what you said...</b></font>

294
